%h1=title 'Invite a friend'
%p Your friend will receive an email, and once they accept you'll be able to view each other's recipes. Cool!
= simple_form_for @friendship do |f|
  = f.error_notification message: 'Please review the problems below'
  = f.input :invitation_email, label_html: { class: 'sr-only' }, placeholder: 'Email'
  = f.submit 'Send request', class: 'btn btn-primary'
